  <com:displayName>Billing System</com:displayName>
  <com:information>The billing system is responsible for tracking and managing billing of services and products. It needs to be informed whenever a chargeable service or product is delivered to the customer. Billing is considered an upstream system.&#xD;
&#xD;
This order component specification for a billing system is used in the decomposition stage that determines the target fulfillment system. Order items are targeted to this billing system based on the BillingToBillingSystem decomposition rule. In this sample cartridge, there is a single billing system. All order items that require a billing function are targeted to this billing system.</com:information>
